d, forming mature <sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604665701072" parent-tag-id="54">tRNA</sd-pretag> ready to bind an <sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604639456710" type="molecule" role="component" category="null">amino acid</sd-pretag> (aa). <graphic href="https://api.sourcedata.io/file.php?panel_id=24071"/></sd-panel><sd-panel panel_id="24072"><strong>C.</strong> Gene region corresponding to <em><sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604643125230" parent-tag-id="2">Rpp30</sd-pretag></em> (RNAse P <sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604639487000" type="molecule" role="normalizing" category="null">protein</sd-pretag> 30, adapted from Flybase). The P-element insertion (<em><sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604643372850" parent-tag-id="2">Rpp30</sd-pretag></em><em><sup><sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604639930680" type="molecule" role="reporter" category="null">PE</sd-pretag></sup></em>, dark grey) and the point mutation Leucine to Proline (<em><sd-pretag id="sdPretag14604643366850" parent-tag-id="2">Rpp30</sd-pretag></em><em><sup>18.2</sup></em>, arrow) are shown. <graphic href="https://api.sourcedata.io/file.php?panel_id=24072"/></sd-panel><sd-panel panel_id="24073"><strong>D.</strong> <sd-tag id="sdTag16" source="sdapi" category="None" entity_type="tissue" role="component" text="Ovaries" ext_ids="UBERON:0002118///UBERON:0002119" ext_dbs="" in_caption="True" ext_names="right ovary///left ovary" ext_tax_ids="" ext_tax_names="" ext_urls="https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon/terms?iri=http%3A%2F%2Fpurl.obolibrary.org%2Fobo%2FUBERON_///https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols/ontologies/uberon/terms?iri=http%3A%2F%2Fpurl.obolibrary.org%2Fobo%2FUBERON_">Ovaries</sd-tag> were dissected, lysed and protein extracts analyzed by <sd-tag id="sdTag17" source="sdapi" category="assay" entity_type="None" role="None" text="Western Blot" ext_ids="BAO_0002424" ext_dbs="" in_caption="True" ext_names="western blot" ext_tax_ids="" ext_tax_names="" ext_urls="https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/BAO/?p=classes&amp;conceptid=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bio